HEADWORD: he-huckleberry
<hw>he-huckleberry</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A deciduous much-branched
shrub (<spn>Lyonia ligustrina</spn>) with dense downy panicles of small
bell-shaped white flowers.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> maleberry, male berry, privet andromeda, <spn>Lyonia
ligustrina</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
